stateDiagram-v2
    direction LR
    [*] --> Healthy

    Healthy: 🟢 HEALTHY<br/>Event loop lag < 50ms<br/>All requests processed normally
    Degraded: 🟡 DEGRADED<br/>Event loop lag 50-200ms<br/>Heavy routes shed traffic
    Critical: 🔴 CRITICAL<br/>Event loop lag > 200ms<br/>All non-essential routes rejected

    Healthy --> Degraded: lag exceeds 50ms
    Degraded --> Critical: lag exceeds 200ms
    Degraded --> Healthy: lag drops below 50ms
    Critical --> Degraded: lag drops below 200ms
